In a message dated 96-05-10 00:26:21 EDT, you write:
 
>If you believe that more "expansive" poetry is not about anything (and
>later you can tell me why you believe that), then why do you agree with
>me that future editions should be more expansive?  Are you adopting a
>poetics of anti-aboutness??
