There are links to EPC, of course, to presses, bookstores, & a few
e-text sites.  I'm most interested in making this a distribution
tool for print; if/when your press or bookstore has a website with
catalog, send me the URL & I'll add it.
 
Wendy
----------------------------------------------------------------
Wendy Battin        http://camel.conncoll.edu/ccother/wjbat/
wjbat@conncoll.edu
wbattin@mit.edu
