I thought this might be useful to at least a few on the Poetics List. I
haven't checked it out enough to know if such special collections as
SUNY/Buffalo's Poetry Room, or UC-San Diego's Archive for New Poetry, or SF
State's American Poetry Archive, are included. One would hope so, as well as
other treasures perhaps. Some of the sites which concern book arts and
alternative book forms may be of interest to those interested in
textual/visual concerns.
 
 
