Keith,
     Thank you, and about time.
     If the question of where our poetics might go from here--which is
surely a preoccupation of Mark's, but also a question vital to  life of
my interest in the list--is put in the terms of where once it was the
only answer usefully elicited is an insistence on where, at least, it
for the moment is.
     Wystan
