Sheila Murphy, Teth, 1991
Karen Mac Cormack, Quirks & Quillets, 1991
Charles Alexander, Hopeful Buildings, 1990
Larry Evers and Felipe S. Molina, Wo=92i Bwikam/Coyote Songs, 1990
bp Nichol, art facts: a book of contexts, 1990
 
 
 
Once again, please send orders directly to me at chax@mtn.org, or to the
address listed in the first part of this message.
 
and thank you,
 
Charles Alexander
Chax Press
