"conventions"? I just read an essay by Peter Burger in his collection
called _The Decline of Modernism"  ... in which he argues that one of the
differnces, or points of modulation in the development of modernism
(the transition from the 18th to the 19th century, from the
Enlightenment to Romanticism) was the shift in poetic composition from
rules to conventions and the different way that positioned the writer
socially and as an "artist".>>
