Se Franc Goutier et sa compaigne Helaine
Eussent ceste doulce vie hantee,
D'oignons, civotz, qui causent forte alaine,
N'acontassent une bise tostee.
 
"If Franc Gontier and his companion Helene
had ever led a life as sweet as this,
they wouldn't give a damn for scallions
or onions which cause bad breath"
 
Franswayze Villon, trans. Anthony Bonner
-- Henri Goulet
